---
title: Garlic Herb Chicken Sausage Tortelloni with Roasted Tomato and Zucchini
description: Why have an average-sized bite of cheesy stuffed pasta, when you could have that same bite slightly bigger? Our chefs wondered the same thing, which is why this dinner features tortelloni (the jumbo cousin of tortellini) coated with a garlicky-herb butter sauce, and topped with roasted tomatoes and zucchini. Toasty panko and Parmesan finish the dish for a flavorful, filling dinner in around 30 minutes. Thanks to tortelloni, you can go big and stay home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6318bb9605cbd66c930a64d2-96083df7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/garlic-herb-chicken-sausage-tortelloni-6318bb9605cbd66c930a64d2-bd72ca43.pdf
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
